comment: В темном углу сидит человек-раб, прячется и по клику баркает

languages.text: "Оно близко... Я чувствую... Оно идет за мной, и мне не спрятаться".
"It is close... I can feel it... It is coming to get me, and there is nowhere to hide."

languages.text: “很近了……我能感觉得到……它来抓我了，我无处可躲。”
languages.original_text: "It is close... I can feel it... It is coming to get me, and there is nowhere to hide."

traits.locale_text: “很近了……我能感觉得到……它来抓我了，我无处可躲。”

languages.text: 「近い…感じる…捕まえにやってくる…、そして隠れる場所なんてどこにもない」
languages.original_text: "It is close... I can feel it... It is coming to get me, and there is nowhere to hide."

languages.text: « Il est près... Je le sens... Il vient me chercher et je ne peux me cacher nulle part. »
languages.original_text: "It is close... I can feel it... It is coming to get me, and there is nowhere to hide."

traits.locale_text: « Il est près... Je le sens... Il vient me chercher et je ne peux me cacher nulle part. »

languages.text: «Está cerca... Puedo sentirlo... Viene a por mí y no tengo dónde esconderme».
languages.original_text: "It is close... I can feel it... It is coming to get me, and there is nowhere to hide."

traits.locale_text: «Está cerca... Puedo sentirlo... Viene a por mí y no tengo dónde esconderme».

languages.text: "Es ist hier ... Ich kann es spüren ... Es kommt, um mich zu holen und verstecken ist zwecklos."
languages.original_text: "It is close... I can feel it... It is coming to get me, and there is nowhere to hide."

languages.text: "Yakında... Hissediyorum... Beni almaya geliyor, saklanarak kaçmam mümkün değil."

traits.locale_text: "Yakında... Hissediyorum... Beni yakalamaya geliyor, saklanacak hiçbir yer yok."
